<plot>Separated by thousands of miles, a Canadian soldier and his young bride transcend an ocean of distance in order to spend one last night together. Set amidst the collapsing borders of World War II, "Alarium" sweeps through the final hours of a tragic love story as the two torn lovers connect from opposite ends of the earth.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?028700</url></doc>
